FBIS3-50953 "drlat007_c_94003" FBIS-LAT-94-007 Document Type:Daily Report 11 Jan 1994 MEXICO Attorney General's Office Announces New Appointments PA1001191994 Mexico City XEW Television Network in Spanish 0430 GMT 7 Jan 94 PA1001191994 Mexico City XEW Television Network Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [From the "24 Hours" newscast] [Text] There have been changes at the Attorney General's Office. Gustavo Hirales Moranes is the new director of the Illicit Crops Erradication Agency and Carlos Santibanez Ramos is director of the Federal Judicial Police's Narcotics Department.
